[log] bash[68] stdout     """
[log] bash[68] stdout     Marks a field as required. For `*args` or a `list[]`, requires at least one item.
[log] bash[68] stdout     Returns:
[log] bash[68] stdout         A value for use with `Annotated[]`, stating that this parameter is required.
[log] bash[68] stdout     """
[log] bash[68] stdout ```
[log] bash[68] stdout **Returns**: A value for use with `Annotated[]`, stating that this parameter is required.
[log] bash[68] stdout #### 7. count() Function - Counted Parameter
