[log] bash[68] stdout #### 8. choices() Function - Choices Parameter
[log] bash[68] stdout **Function**: Specifies a fixed set of values that a parameter is allowed to be. If a parameter is an `enum.Enum` type, this
[log] bash[68] stdout logic is already used to restrict the inputs to be one of the enum entries.
