[log] bash[68] stdout     @property
[log] bash[68] stdout     def is_optional(self) -> bool:
[log] bash[68] stdout         return self in [InputMethod.OPTIONAL_POSITIONAL, InputMethod.OPTION]
[log] bash[68] stdout ```
[log] bash[68] stdout #### 50. Type Aliases
